                     <interp inst="t17870221-89-person907" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            ,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17870221-89-verdict404" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870221-89-verdict404" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Each to be <rs id="t17870221-89-punish405" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870221-89-punish405" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870221-89-punish405" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870221-89-defend892 t17870221-89-punish405"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870221-89-defend896 t17870221-89-punish405"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs> and <rs id="t17870221-89-punish406" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870221-89-punish406" type="punishmentCategory" value="imprison"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870221-89-defend892 t17870221-89-punish406"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870221-89-defend896 t17870221-89-punish406"></join>
               imprisoned one week
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>SARAH YORK, alias HORSEMAN,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17870221-89-verdict407" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870221-89-verdict407" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the third Middlesex Jury before Mr. ROSE.</p>
